00:56:55.020 --> 00:56:59.930
and this is the big enchilada, as they say,
in that you

00:56:59.930 --> 00:57:04.270
need to be--, disclose enough about yourself
so that you

00:57:04.270 --> 00:57:07.980
feel comfortable, and if you're a leader,
I would argue

00:57:07.980 --> 00:57:10.230
you have to disclose about -- enough about
yourself to

00:57:10.230 --> 00:57:12.530
encourage others to feel comfortable about
you and to

00:57:12.530 --> 00:57:16.570
know you. We're always making a judgment about
where to

00:57:16.570 --> 00:57:19.980
draw that line. There's certain things about
me I could

00:57:19.980 --> 00:57:22.810
tell you that would make you laugh, would
make you

00:57:22.810 --> 00:57:26.240
understand me better a little bit, but you
don't need to

00:57:26.240 --> 00:57:28.930
